    # Knowledge Graph
    
    A network of entities connected by relationships.
    Rendering your notes as a graph reveals clusters 
    and bridges you would never notice in a list.
    This is exactly what the Spectacles lens visualizes in 3D.
    
    #concept
    
    See also: [[Hypertext]], [[Embeddings]], [[Obsidian]]

